1297
01:13:17.992 --> 01:13:21.332
He'll be able to talk
about his experiences

1298
01:13:21.398 --> 01:13:23.102
through poetry.

1299
01:13:23.169 --> 01:13:25.139
♪♪ ♪♪

1300
01:13:25.206 --> 01:13:27.812
WARREN: "Love is trust.
