1306
01:13:41.338 --> 01:13:44.512
WARREN: Love is a promise.
Keep love alive.

1307
01:13:44.579 --> 01:13:46.950
♪♪ ♪♪

1308
01:13:47.017 --> 01:13:49.989
Know who you love before you
define who to hate.

