01:13:50.056 --> 01:13:51.959
♪♪ ♪♪

1310
01:13:52.026 --> 01:13:54.364
The love you give
is the love you get.

1311
01:13:54.431 --> 01:13:57.470
♪♪ ♪♪

1312
01:13:57.538 --> 01:14:01.344
No matter where you stand.
